    "desc": "NEO LMS is an award-winning intelligent learning platform (ILP) used by schools and universities worldwide. NEO LMS is a complete solution that incorporates all the essential tools education institutions need to support efficient teaching and learning.",
    "navbar": "SELECT YOUR LANGUAGE\nCOMPANY\nCONTACT SALES\nBLOG\nSUPPORT\nLOG IN",
    "text": "SELECT YOUR LANGUAGE\nCOMPANY\nCONTACT SALES\nBLOG\nSUPPORT\nLOG IN\nSolutions\nShow submenu for Solutions\nProducts\nShow submenu for Products\nCustomers\nShow submenu for Customers\nResources\nShow submenu for Resources\nSchedule a demo\nJanuary 19, 2023\nCYPHER LEARNING presents 24h Education - a global, virtual education marathon for 24 hrs!\nGet your ticket now!\nNEO LMS for K-20\nInstitutions worldwide use NEO LMS to build engaging content and manage all learning activities.\nSchedule a demo\nTake a tour\nWhy choose NEO LMS\nA complete solution for teachers, students, and school admins\nUser-friendly platform\nNEO LMS has an intuitive design that makes it easy to use, even by a first-grader.\nInclusive elearning\nOnline learning has no limitations thanks to our accessibility features.\nIntelligent\nNEO LMS saves you time by choosing learning paths for students based on their goals.\nMobile first\nUse our mobile apps to enjoy a great learning experience, anytime, anywhere.\nTrusted by schools and universities around the world\nAll-in-one learning platform\nWe have the best solution for each type of academic institution\nK-12\nOur platform supports every student on their learning journey: from kindergarten to college.\nNEO for K-12\nHigher Ed\nBuild personalized classes and prepare students for real-world careers with NEO LMS.\nNEO for Higher Ed\nFOR TEACHERS\nMake teaching a breeze\nTeachers are the pillars of education. NEO LMS helps them build high-quality classes and frees up their time so they can focus on having a greater impact on their students.\nContent authoring tool\nEasily create engaging content for your classes without any prior technical knowledge.\nCompetency-based learning\nUse adaptive learning to personalize student content based on their goals and performance.\nEvaluation\nChoose from a variety of assignment types and centralize all results in our powerful gradebook.\nAutomation\nSave time by setting goals when students enroll in a class or fall behind mastery levels.\n92% of surveyed schools agreed with the following statement:\n“NEO has transformed our institution, making it easy for teachers to create online classes and for students to stay engaged and have an enjoyable learning experience anytime, anywhere.”\nSource: TechValidate survey of 153 clients of NEO LMS\n92%\nFOR STUDENTS\nLearn together and have fun\nStudents have broad academic expectations. Design learning that is fun, engaging, and prepares them for real-world careers.\nGamification\nAward students with points & badges using class games to make learning fun.\nPersonalized learning\nGain mastery of the concepts taught and understand where you need to improve.\nCollaboration\nChat with students and faculty members on projects, in public or private groups.\nPublic profiles\nAllow students to showcase their achievements such as badges and certificates.\n73% of surveyed schools selected NEO as their LMS due to the platform being an all-in-one solution for online teaching and learning.\nSource: TechValidate survey of 154 clients of NEO LMS\n73%\nFOR SCHOOL MANAGEMENT\nRealize your institution’s success\nGet a bird’s-eye view of the whole campus and how the overall teaching staff is performing to save time on administrative tasks, automate workflows, and supervise all school activities.\nAnalytics\nGet insights on classes, assignments, and students in an instant.\nOrganizations\nGroup campuses together and manage them in a single account.\nParent access\nAccess children’s grades and communicate with the school staff.\nCustomized portal\nCreate a custom portal to showcase your school and communicate news.\nTake a tour of NEO\n94% of surveyed organizations rate the implementation of NEO as being better compared to the competition.\nSource: TechValidate survey of 150 clients of NEO LMS\n94%\nOur recognitions\nTo testify our dedication as a learning management system\nFast implementation\nWe’ll help you get started with NEO LMS in no time with:\nFull support on every step of the implementation\nOn-site training by our edtech experts\nMigrating your existing content\nCreating custom e-learning content\nAre you ready to try NEO LMS for your institution?\nSchedule a demo\n7250 Dallas Parkway, Suite 400, Plano, TX 75024\n+1 972 634 3390\nView all social channels\nPRODUCTS\nNEO\nMATRIX\nINDIE\nPartners\nEdTech Center\nCompare products\nWhat is an LMS?\nWhat is an ILP?\nGEMs\nSOLUTIONS\nK-12\nHigher ed\nEmployee training\nSkills development\nTraining organizations\nFinancial institutions\nHealthcare associations\nPublishers\nContent creators\nCOMPANY\nAbout us\nContact us\nCareers HIRING\nAwards\nNews\nEvents\n24h Education REGISTER\nFAQ\nResellers\nCYPHER Voices\nRESOURCES\nAll resources\nVideos\nGuides\nWebinars\nBrochures\nInfographics\nWhite papers\nLMS Comparisons\nBlog\nLanguages Data processing Cookie policy Subscription agreement Sitemap Status",
